Type of Feat: General
You have mastered the use of heavy armor, maximizing its protective qualities while moving more easily in it.
Prerequisite: Heavy Armor Optimization, Base Attack Bonus +8
Benefit: When you are wearing heavy armor, lessen the armor check penalty by 3 and increase the armor bonus by 2. This is done as a +skill bonus to (Hide, Move Silently, and Tumble) and a +2 Dodge AC bonus. This bonus replaces the one from Heavy Armor Optimization.
Special: A fighter can choose Greater Heavy Armor Optimization as one of his bonus fighter feats.
Use: Automatic.